Congo-Kinshasa (DR Congo; formerly Zaire) 1998

National Championship (LINAFOOT)

Final Regional Qualification Tournament 

Poule Kinshasa
DC Motema Pembe 3-0   AS Sucrière

Table:
 1.DC Motema Pembe (Kinshasa)           6
 2.AS Sucrière (Kwilu Ngongo)           1
 3.AS Ndombe (Bandundu?)                0

NB: DC Motema Pembe qualified

Sous-Poule Kananga

Table:
