 4.TP Mazembe        6  1  2  3   7- 8  5  

DC Motema Pembe champions 1998.


National Cup 1998

Final  
AS Dragons (Kinshasa)    1-0 AS Sucrière (Kwilu Ngongo)
  [75' Tandioyi]


